<BR></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-a" mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>Jake...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$???$<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(You see a stranger. That must be Jake)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-b" mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>I'm... from the future. I know all about you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>
...? Do you know me? I don't think we've met...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-c" mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>Can you stop what you're doing right now?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>
The future...? Haha... You're a funny little lady.<BR>
What brings a little lady from the future to such a dangerous place?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-d" mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>You being a Dragon Follower....</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>
What do you mean stop? I don't have a clue what you're talking about...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-d" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-e" mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>You're... going to die soon.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>
..........<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake smiles)</FONT><BR>
Why would a little girl like you tell me this?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-f" mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>(Show him the data from the communicator)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>
Die soon...?<BR>
Haha... that's interesting.<BR>
May I ask who will kill me and how I'll die?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-f" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-g" mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>It's not too late. If you change your mind...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake becomes silent after seeing the data. Jake's face darkens, but quickly regains his smile)</FONT><BR>I see. I'll get killed by my brother... Haha....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-g" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-h" mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>I don't understand. Why...? Even though you know you'll die?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Jake quietly shakes his head)</FONT><BR>No.... I won't stop nor turn around.<BR>And, I'll faithfully accomplish my last duty.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-h" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-i" mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>Well.... Maybe I'm capricious, or maybe too stubborn... Haha....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-i" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-j" mid="97"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="96"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>
My life was so empty and meaningless when I was a child.<BR>
I was only alive for the sake of being alive. So when I felt even a slightest hint of warmth, I desperately followed it, thinking that it could tell me why I'm alive.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-j" image="QN_Jake.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-k" mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>But, this world was too twisted to begin with.<BR>
I was always surrounded by a thick layer of darkness, and anger and hatred towards the world were all that filled me up.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-k" image="QN_Npc_Edan.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-l" mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>You think of Edan so dearly. Then why....</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake$<BR>But someone rescued me from the abyss of hatred.<BR>A person with such a pure soul… My brother and my companion…<BR>I met Edan, my precious brother…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-1-l" image="QN_Npc_Edan.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n537_cleric_jake-1-camerawork" mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>What are you saying…?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake${action:Talk}<BR>Haha... If he had taken the wrong path, I might have stopped. But....<BR>Fortunately, he has grown to be a great cleric...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-1" image="QW_10.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="74"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>
Ahh... I'm so frustrated.<BR>
Should I just go? Or not?<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Hurry to Frost Wind Forest)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
