      <talk_question mid="75"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan$<BR>
We're one step too late....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n539_angelica-1" image="QN_Npc_Angelica.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="76"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica$<BR>Ahh~~~!! I could have caught him~!<BR>Sly Dragon Follower, shame on you for running away like that~!!!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Angelica is furious)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n538_edan-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Edan${action:Talk}<BR>We're one step too late....</html>]]></talk_question>
