   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n539_angelica-2-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n539_angelica-2-b" mid="52"><![CDATA[<html>Calm down....</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica$<BR>
I'm already annoyed that someone was suspicious that I might be the one who stole the Orb! This is all Edan's fault. He's so slow!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n539_angelica-2-b" image="QN_Npc_Angelica.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n539_angelica-3" mid="54"><![CDATA[<html>First, let's get out of here.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica${action:Talk}<BR>But, where does this path lead to?<BR>I think I have read it somewhere…<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Angelica thinks hard)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n537_cleric_jake-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="98"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Jake${action:Talk}<BR>Haha... If he had taken the wrong path, I might have stopped. But....<BR>Fortunately, he has grown to be a great cleric...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n539_angelica-3" image="QW_FrostHill.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica$<BR>Okay, let's go back to <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Hill</FONT> for now.<BR>Since we can't go through that door, let's find another way.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n535_angelica-3" image="QN_Npc_Edan.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n535_angelica-3-a" mid="58"><![CDATA[<html>(Frail...?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="57"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica$<BR>
<FONT color=#a82424>Edan</FONT> went ahead saying that he had to report this to Master Cleric Thomas, that cold-hearted bastard!<BR>
How could he leave a frail woman like me alone like this!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n535_angelica-3-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n535_angelica-3-b" mid="60"><![CDATA[<html>It's a dangerous place for kids....</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="59"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica${action:Talk}<BR>I'm just about to remember where the Frost Wind Forest leads to!<BR>In the old days, I've been there with Tara after skipping an Introduction to Magic class!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n535_angelica-3-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n535_angelica-3-c" mid="62"><![CDATA[<html>Marian's Shrine.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica$<BR>
..........<BR>
It's funny hearing that from you, kid.<BR>
Anyway~! I think it led to...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n535_angelica-3-c" image="QW_11.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n535_angelica-3-d" mid="64"><![CDATA[<html>As I've told you before, I'm from the future...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica$<BR>
Yes! <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT>....<BR>
What? You knew?!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n535_angelica-3-d" image="QW_11.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n535_angelica-3-e" mid="67"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="65"><![CDATA[<html>$Sorceress Angelica$<BR>
